---
title: South Indian John Dory & Cauliflower Curry with Garlic Rice & Cucumber Raita
description: Dive into a dish that captures the flavours of South Indian cuisine with our John dory and South Indian cauliflower curry. Succulent fish fillets are gentry pan-fried and served with a mild cauliflower curry, delivering a meal which is sure to satisfy.
